messages.messageBody:
My kids have been collecting the state quarters as they come
out. The holder they have for them has two slots for each state, one
for Denver minted coins and one for Philadelphia minted coins. Thing
is that Philadelphia minted coins are pretty scarce out here on the
west coast. The first couple of years we traded with a friend who
lived back east, but they moved back to California.

So...I was wondering if some other east coast family would be
interested in trading us some Philly minted state quarters for some
Denver ones. We recently had lots of coins come into our lives so we
have a pretty complete set of Denver ones. Email me off list if
you're interested.

Pam
